creator: Emplate ApS
descriptionHtml:
As an employee in a store within a shopping mall using Emplate, you are able to use this app for creating campaigns.

You have access to insightful data showing you which campaigns generates the most views and visits to your store.

If you haven't received login information, please ask your contact within the mall.
descriptionShort: This app can only be used by shops in malls who use Emplate.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This update of the app introduces a set of terms and conditions for use of the app.
It is important that you read these before continuing the use of the app.
